{"tid":769171,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[放榜] OU NURSING過來人問答區","createTime":"2018-08-06T03:29:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T05:29:41.000Z","uid":145629,"like":13,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"6768948f4db0184b9fdb6c5c1e3e45c9e862494c","tid":769171,"uid":145629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T03:29:07.000Z","msg":"上年22分入左ou general nursing sssdp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n適逢今年各位師弟妹放榜，諗返起上年好迷茫，又覺得入左ou唔開心又唔知入左要做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n印象中上年都有呢類po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都幾安撫到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以各位師弟妹有乜都可以問架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbetween 其實讀左一年都覺得唔錯，師弟妹唔洗太頹，ou個名係唔好聽，但nursing都還算做得唔錯嘅，入左黎就比心機讀落去都包你唔會餓死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d39809733a7641475d0bbe3a6e39198e4807ffdd","tid":769171,"uid":27601,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T03:32:27.000Z","msg":"樓豬好撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a3e3cf0f0d6c9b19ecd1cbc2501fd2b2a316725","tid":769171,"uid":145629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d39809733a7641475d0bbe3a6e39198e4807ffdd","tid":769171,"uid":27601,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T03:32:27.000Z","msg":"樓豬好撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T03:37:07.000Z","msg":"你呢？你係咪都係今年入左ou nursing呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"383f981a16787a28083e91c2cd60b8d45615baa2","tid":769171,"uid":27601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2a3e3cf0f0d6c9b19e